quiz.name: Precourse Self-Assessment
quiz.intro:
How much do you know about or focus on contextualized instruction?
Take a moment to reflect on your current lesson planning process and your understanding of contextualized instruction. For each factor, select the rating that best reflects your current lesson planning process. When you are finished, click on “Check my answers” to view your score and suggestions to increase your skill and knowledge.

feedback.feedbacktext: On the right track! You have a solid understanding of contextualized instruction and its link to adult career pathways.
You are almost there! Check out the extended learning activities in the course to continue building your skills. You can also take notes with the note-taking guide.
Be sure to explore the resources and extended learning activities listed in each section. You can also take notes with the note-taking guide.
